            <div type="transcript" id="F343A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>When we stand on the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 tops of Things -</l>
                    <l>And like the Trees, look down, </l>
                    <l>The smoke all cleared away<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 from it - </l>
                    <l>And mirrorrs on the scene - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Just laying light - no soul<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 will wink</l>
                    <l>Except it have the flaw - </l>
                    <l>The Sound ones, like the<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Hills -<add type="alternate" extent="shall stand -">stand up -</add>
 shall stand - </l>
                    <l>No lightning,<add type="alternate" extent="scares">drives -</add>
 scares away - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Perfect, nowhere be<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 afraid -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>They bear their<add type="alternate" extent="dauntless">fearless - &amp;#x2022; tranquil -</add>
 dauntless<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Heads,</l>
                    <l>Where others, dare not<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
<add type="alternate" extent="go at noon,">walk at noon -</add>
 go at noon, </l>
                    <l>Protected by their deeds - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Stars dare shine<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 occasionally </l>
                    <l>Opon a spotted World - </l>
                    <l>And Suns, go surer, for<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 their Proof,</l>
                    <l>As if<add type="alternate" extent="an axle, held">a muscle - held</add>
 an axle, held - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
